text:
Ayça Aykaç (born 27 February 1996) is a Turkish volleyball player.
She played at the 2015 FIVB Volleyball Women's U20 World Championship, 2016 FIVB Volleyball Women's Club World Championship, 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's Club World Championship, 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's U20 World Championship, and 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's Club World Championship.
She played for VakıfBank S.K.
